Taking camp at nightfall I realize something keeps telling me that these mortals are not worth my effort.  From the senseless, purely evil Draconians to the awe-inspiring, powerful-in-every-way Dragons.  They too are mortals, and hopefully they will stand by me in my cause.  My eyes close, I slowly drift away, the knight I had fought with on my mind.  Maybe... I can make this... journey more... interesting.
