Razel unexpectedly stops at the first sound of my voice, though finishes his quiet prayer before slowly rising, and still facing the altar, he bows to it, a gesture of reverence, supposedly, before he faces me. "{DYes, my Lord..?{x" He says, the words evenly spoken, with a humble tone.
 
