Showing no facial expression, Razel nods slowly, the only response vague, with his eyes staring blankly into mine, as if in thought, of anything.. contemplation, or otherwise.
 
I nodded once, leveled, and measured perfectly, graceful even, as far as a nod goes. Though the odd expression of my own, even if hardly visible, unchanging. "{DI will be stepping down, as Lord of Night, Lord Razel..{x" Razel's interest seemingly perked with such simple words, though he chose to hide it. "{DThe position will be passed down to you; and I will be posted in Neraka.. the Queen wishes for me to revive her armies..{x" I said surely, my tone quite smooth, and convincing.
 
