The grey figure decided he would take a chance, and risk everything on a simple loud crack. He pulled out his form of a whip. A bloodied, human intestine that seemed to have random specs of black upon it, obviously some sort of disease. The intestine reeked heavily of the smell of death, and disease as the grey figures hand tightened around the end of it, blood dripping from the pressure, onto the cold, wet mountain.
